ihm_struct_assembly.description:
Structure of the SLC26Dg dimer determined by integrating the experimental 
  structure of the monomer, spatial restraints from DEER/PELDOR EPR, MD simulations, and 
  spin-label rotamer refinement using an ensemble refinement approach (BioEn).
